  <para style="mt1">MARŨA MA KEERĨ MA PAŨLŨ KŨRĨ TIMOTHEO</para>
  <para style="imt1">Ũhoro wa Ibuku Rĩĩrĩ</para>
  <para style="ip">Marũa-inĩ maya ma Keerĩ ma Timotheo, Paũlũ aandĩkĩire Timotheo akĩmũtaara ta mwana wake thĩinĩ wa wĩtĩkio. Paũlũ nĩahooyagĩra Timotheo kaingĩ (1:2, 3) tondũ nĩendaga atuĩke mũthigari mwega wa Jesũ Kristũ, na erute kũũmĩrĩria mathĩĩna (2:1, 3). Paũlũ nĩagwetete nyina wa Timotheo na cũwe na marĩĩtwa mao, o na akaririkania Timotheo ũrĩa aamũigĩrĩire moko arĩ kĩonereria atĩ Roho wa Ngai nĩarĩmũtongoragia wĩra-inĩ wake.</para>
  <para style="ip">Paũlũ nĩataarire Timotheo igũrũ rĩkoniĩ matukũ maritũ marĩa maakirie gũkinya, na ũrĩa andũ magaatiganĩria ũhoro ũrĩa wa ma na marege gwĩtĩkia atĩ Jesũ nĩwe Mwathani. Eerire Timotheo ndagatigithĩrie kũhunjia ndũmĩrĩri ya Ngai (4:2).</para>
  <para style="ip">Paũlũ nĩamenyaga atĩ mũtũũrĩre wake warĩ hakuhĩ gũkinya mũthia, no nĩamenyaga atĩ nĩakarĩhwo nĩ ũndũ wa wĩhokeku wake (4:6-8).</para>
  <para style="iot">Mwandĩki</para>
  <para style="im">Ibuku rĩĩrĩ rĩandĩkirwo nĩ Mũtũmwo Paũlũ.</para>
  <para style="iot">Ũrĩa Ibuku Rĩĩrĩ Rĩgayanĩtio</para>
  <para style="io1">· Paũlũ gũcookeria Timotheo ngaatho <char style="ior"><ref loc="2TI 1:1-5">1:1-5</ref></char></para>
  <para style="io1">· Paũlũ kũhe Timotheo ũtaaro <char style="ior"><ref loc="2TI 1:6-2:2">1:6–2:2</ref></char></para>
  <para style="io1">· Gũtaarĩria ũhoro wa ndungata njĩhokeku <char style="ior"><ref loc="2TI 2:3-26">2:3-26</ref></char></para>
  <para style="io1">· Mĩnyamaro ĩrĩa yatanyagwo <char style="ior"><ref loc="2TI 3:1-17">3:1-17</ref></char></para>
  <para style="io1">· Ciugo cia mũthia cia Paũlũ <char style="ior"><ref loc="2TI 4:1-22">4:1-22</ref></char>.</para>
  <para style="ie"/>
  <chapter number="1" style="c"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="2CO 1:1">2Akor 1:1</ref>; <ref loc="EPH 3:6">Aef 3:6</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩ niĩ Paũlũ, mũtũmwo wa Kristũ Jesũ nĩ ũndũ wa kwenda kwa Ngai. Ndatũmirwo nĩ Ngai kũringana na kĩĩranĩro kĩa muoyo ũrĩa ũrĩ thĩinĩ wa Kristũ Jesũ,</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="2" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:2 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1TI 1:2">1Tim 1:2</ref>; <ref loc="ROM 1:7">Arom 1:7</ref></char>
    </note>Ndakwandĩkĩra wee Timotheo, o we mũrũ wakwa nyendete mũno:</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">Wega, na tha, na thayũ kuuma kũrĩ Ngai Ithe witũ, na Kristũ Jesũ Mwathani witũ, irogĩa nawe.</para>
  <para style="s1">Kũũmĩrĩrio Gũtuĩka Mwĩhokeku</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:3 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ROM 1:8">Arom 1:8</ref>; <ref loc="ACT 23:1">Atũm 23:1</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩnjookagĩria Ngai ngaatho, ũrĩa niĩ ndungatagĩra ndĩ na thamiri ĩtarĩ na ũcuuke, o ta ũrĩa maithe makwa ma tene meekaga, o ngĩkũririkanaga hĩndĩ ciothe ũtukũ na mũthenya, mahooya-inĩ makwa itegũtigithĩria. <verse number="4" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:4 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2TI 4:9">2Tim 4:9</ref></char></note>Nĩndĩĩriragĩria mũno gũkuona, ndaririkana maithori maku, nĩgeetha njiyũrwo nĩ gĩkeno. <verse number="5" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:5 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 16:1">Atũm 16:1</ref>; <ref loc="1TI 1:5">1Tim 1:5</ref></char></note>Nĩndirikanĩtio ũhoro wa wĩtĩkio waku ũrĩa ũtarĩ ũhinga, o ta ũrĩa watũire na cũguo Loisi, na nyũkwa Eunike, na rĩu nĩnjĩtĩkĩtie atĩ wĩtĩkio ũcio ũrĩ o thĩinĩ waku. <verse number="6" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:6 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1TI 4:14">1Tim 4:14</ref></char></note>Nĩ ũndũ wa gĩtũmi gĩkĩ nĩngũkũririkania atĩ ũhuhagĩrĩrie kĩheo kĩrĩa ũheetwo nĩ Ngai, kĩrĩa wagĩire nakĩo rĩrĩa ndakũigĩrĩire moko. <verse number="7" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:7 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 8:15">Arom 8:15</ref>; <ref loc="ISA 11:2">Isa 11:2</ref></char></note>Nĩgũkorwo Ngai ndaatũheire roho wa gũtwĩkagĩra guoya, no aatũheire roho wa gũtwĩkĩra hinya, na wa wendani, na wa ũũgĩ wa kwĩnyiita maũndũ-inĩ mothe.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:8 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EPH 3:1">Aef 3:1</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio ndũkanaconoke ũkiumbũra ũira wa Mwathani witũ, kana ũconoke nĩ ũndũ wakwa niĩ njohetwo nĩ ũndũ wake. No nyiitanĩra na niĩ kũnyariirwo nĩ ũndũ wa Ũhoro-ũrĩa-Mwega, nĩ ũndũ nĩũrĩheagwo hinya nĩ Ngai. <verse number="9" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:9 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 11:4">Arom 11:4</ref>; <ref loc="EPH 2:9">Aef 2:9</ref></char></note>Ngai nĩwe watũhonokirie na agĩtwĩtĩra mũtũũrĩre mũtheru, ti tondũ wa ũndũ twĩkĩte, no nĩ ũndũ wa ũrĩa aatanyĩte gwĩka na nĩ ũndũ wa wega wake. Twaheirwo wega ũyũ thĩinĩ wa Kristũ Jesũ mbere ya kĩambĩrĩria gĩa thĩ, <verse number="10" style="v"/>no wega ũcio rĩu nĩũguũranĩirio nĩ ũndũ wa kuonekana kwa Mũhonokia witũ, Kristũ Jesũ, ũrĩa waniinire gĩkuũ, na akĩrehe muoyo o na ũhoro wa kwaga kũbutha akĩũiga ũtheri-inĩ nĩ ũndũ wa Ũhoro-ũrĩa-Mwega. <verse number="11" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:11 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1TI 2:7">1Tim 2:7</ref></char></note>Na nĩ ũndũ wa Ũhoro-ũcio-Mwega-rĩ, nĩndamũrirwo nduĩke mũhunjia, na mũtũmwo, na mũrutani waguo. <verse number="12" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:12 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1TI 6:20">1Tim 6:20</ref></char></note>Ũhoro ũcio nĩguo ũtũmĩte nyamarĩke ũguo. No ndiconokaga, tondũ ũrĩa niĩ njĩtĩkĩtie nĩndĩmũũĩ, na ndĩ na ma atĩ arĩ na ũhoti wa kũgitĩra kĩrĩa ndĩmwĩhokeire o nginya rĩrĩa mũthenya ũcio ũgaakinya.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:13 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1TI 1:14">1Tim 1:14</ref>; <ref loc="TIT 1:9">Tit 1:9</ref></char>
    </note>Rũmia ũhoro ũrĩa waiguire kuuma kũrĩ niĩ, ũrĩ kĩonereria kĩa ũrutani mwega, ũrĩ na wĩtĩkio na wendani thĩinĩ wa Kristũ Jesũ. <verse number="14" style="v"/>Menyerera ũndũ ũrĩa mwega ũrĩa wehokeirwo, na ũũmenyerere ũteithĩtio nĩ Roho Mũtheru ũrĩa ũikaraga thĩinĩ witũ.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v"/>Wee nĩũĩ atĩ andũ othe thĩinĩ wa bũrũri wa Asia nĩmandiganĩirie, o hamwe na Fugelo, na Herimogene.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:16 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="2TI 4:19">2Tim 4:19</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Mwathani aroiguĩra andũ a nyũmba ya Onesiforo tha tondũ aananyamarũra kaingĩ na ndaconokire nĩ ũndũ wakwa kuohwo na mĩnyororo. <verse number="17" style="v"/>Nowe, hĩndĩ ĩrĩa ookire Roma, nĩanjaririe na kĩyo o nginya akĩnyona. <verse number="18" style="v"/>Mwathani aroĩtĩkĩra atĩ akaaiguĩrwo tha nĩ Mwathani mũthenya ũcio wakinya! Wee nĩũĩ wega mũno ũrĩa aandeithirie na njĩra nyingĩ rĩrĩa ndaarĩ Efeso.</para>
  <chapter number="2" style="c"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">2:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EPH 6:10">Aef 6:10</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nĩ ũndũ wa ũguo, wee mũrũ wakwa-rĩ, gĩa na hinya thĩinĩ wa wega wa Ngai ũrĩa ũrĩ thĩinĩ wa Kristũ Jesũ. <verse number="2" style="v"/>Namo maũndũ marĩa waiguire ngĩaria mbere ya aira aingĩ-rĩ, mehokere andũ ehokeku arĩa ũũĩ atĩ no mahote kũruta andũ angĩ. <verse number="3" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:3 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1TI 1:18">1Tim 1:18</ref></char></note>Ũmĩrĩria gũthĩĩnĩka hamwe na ithuĩ ta ũrĩ mũthigari mwega wa Kristũ Jesũ. <verse number="4" style="v"/>Gũtirĩ mũndũ ũrutaga wĩra wa mũthigari ũngĩĩohania na maũndũ matarĩ ma ũũthigari: we endaga o gũkenia mũnene wake ũrĩa ũmwathaga. <verse number="5" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:5 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 9:25">1Akor 9:25</ref></char></note>Ũguo no taguo, mũndũ ũrĩa ũhanyũkaga mathako-inĩ ma mahenya ndangĩheo thũmbĩ ya ũhootani atathaakĩte kũringana na ũrĩa gwathanĩtwo. <verse number="6" style="v"/>Ningĩ-rĩ, mũrĩmi ũrĩa wĩnogagia akĩrĩma mũgũnda nĩ we wagĩrĩirwo gũtuĩka wa mbere kwamũkĩra maciaro maguo. <verse number="7" style="v"/>Cũranagia maũndũ marĩa ndĩroiga, nĩgũkorwo Mwathani nĩarĩkũũhĩgagia maũndũ-inĩ macio mothe.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">2:8 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ROM 2:16">Arom 2:16</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Atĩrĩrĩ, ririkanaga Jesũ Kristũ, ũrĩa wariũkirio akiuma kũrĩ arĩa akuũ, na aarĩ wa rũciaro rwa Daudi, kũringana na Ũhoro-ũrĩa-Mwega, ũrĩa niĩ hunjagia. <verse number="9" style="v"/>Ũhoro ũcio nĩguo niĩ nyariiragĩrwo o nginya ngohwo na mĩnyororo ta ndĩ mũgeri ngero. No kiugo kĩa Ngai ti kĩohe. <verse number="10" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:10 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 1:24">1Akor 1:24</ref></char></note>Nĩ ũndũ ũcio, niĩ nĩnyũmagĩrĩria maũndũ mothe nĩ ũndũ wa arĩa aamũre, nĩgeetha o nao megĩĩre na ũhonokio ũrĩa ũrĩ thĩinĩ wa Kristũ Jesũ, na magĩe na riiri wa tene na tene.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>Ũhoro ũyũ nĩ wa kwĩhokeka, atĩrĩ:</para>
  <para style="q1">Angĩkorwo nĩtwakuire hamwe nake-rĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">o na gũtũũra nĩtũgaatũũra muoyo hamwe nake;</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">2:12 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 10:33">Math 10:33</ref>
      </char>
    </note>na tũngĩkirĩrĩria-rĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">o na gũthamaka nĩtũgaathamaka hamwe nake.</para>
  <para style="q1">No tũngĩmũkaana-rĩ,</para>
  <para style="q2">o nake nĩagatũkaana;</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">2:13 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ROM 3:3">Arom 3:3</ref>
      </char>
    </note>na tũngĩaga kwĩhokeka,</para>
  <para style="q2">we egũtũũra arĩ o mwĩhokeku,</para>
  <para style="q2">nĩgũkorwo we ndangĩhota gwĩkaana.</para>
  <para style="s1">Mũruti Wĩra Mwĩtĩkĩrĩku harĩ Ngai</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>Ririkanagia andũ maũndũ macio. Makaanagie ũrĩ mbere ya Ngai nĩguo matige gũkararanĩria ndeto itarĩ kĩene; ndeto icio itirĩ kĩguni, no gũthũkia ithũkagia arĩa maciiguaga. <verse number="15" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:15 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EPH 1:13">Aef 1:13</ref>; <ref loc="JAS 1:18">Jak 1:18</ref></char></note>Geria mũno wĩonanagie harĩ Ngai wĩ mwĩtĩkĩrĩku, na wĩ mũruti-wĩra ũtarĩ ũndũ ũngĩmũconora, na ũrutanage ũhoro ũrĩa wa ma ũrũngĩrĩirie. <verse number="16" style="v"/>Ehagĩrĩra mĩario ĩtarĩ ya gwĩtigĩra Ngai, tondũ arĩa mekenagia na ndeto icio makĩragĩrĩria kwaga gwĩtigĩra Ngai. <verse number="17" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:17 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1TI 1:20">1Tim 1:20</ref></char></note>Ũrutani wao ũtheaga ta kĩronda kĩa ndĩĩra. Amwe ao nĩ Humenayo, na Fileto, <verse number="18" style="v"/>arĩa maturuurĩte na magatiga ũhoro wa ma. Moigaga atĩ ũhoro wa kũriũka nĩũrĩkĩtie kũhĩtũka, na nĩ mathũkĩtie wĩtĩkio wa andũ amwe. <verse number="19" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:19 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 10:14">Joh 10:14</ref>; <ref loc="EXO 33:12">Thaam 33:12</ref></char></note>No rĩrĩ, mũthingi ũrĩa mũrũmu wa Ngai nĩwĩhaandĩte wega naguo wĩkĩrĩtwo rũũri na ciugo ici: “Mwathani nĩoĩ andũ arĩa marĩ ake,” na ningĩ atĩrĩ, “Ũrĩa wothe uumbũraga rĩĩtwa rĩa Mwathani no nginya agarũrũke atigane na waganu.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">2:20 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ROM 9:21">Arom 9:21</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Thĩinĩ wa nyũmba yothe nene-rĩ, to indo cia thahabu na betha ikoragwo kuo ciiki, no nĩ kũrĩ indo cia mĩtĩ na cia rĩũmba; imwe nĩ cia wĩra ũrĩa mũtĩĩe, na imwe nĩ cia wĩra ũrĩa ũtangĩtĩĩka. <verse number="21" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:21 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2TI 3:17">2Tim 3:17</ref></char></note>Mũndũ angĩĩtheria kuuma kũrĩ maũndũ macio matangĩtĩĩka, no atuĩke ta kĩndũ gĩa kũruta wĩra wa gĩtĩĩo, kĩndũ gĩtherie, kĩrĩa kĩagĩrĩire Mwathi wa nyũmba ĩyo na kĩhaarĩirio gĩa kũrutaga wĩra o wothe mwega. <verse number="22" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:22 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1TI 1:5">1Tim 1:5</ref></char></note>Na rĩrĩ, ũragĩra merirĩria mooru ma wĩthĩ, na ũthingatage ũthingu, na wĩtĩkio, na wendani, na thayũ, mũrĩ hamwe na arĩa makayagĩra Mwathani marĩ na ngoro theru. <verse number="23" style="v"/>Reganaga na ngarari cia ũrimũ na cia ũkĩĩgu, tondũ nĩũĩ irehage ngũĩ. <verse number="24" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:24 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1TI 3:2">1Tim 3:2</ref>, <ref loc="1TI 3:3">3</ref></char></note>Nayo ndungata ya Ngai ndĩagĩrĩirwo nĩ gũtuĩka ya ngũĩ; handũ ha ũguo, yagĩrĩirwo nĩgũtuĩka ya gũtuga mũndũ o wothe, na ĩrĩ mũndũ wĩ na ũhoti wa kũrutana, na ĩrĩ mũndũ mũkirĩrĩria. <verse number="25" style="v"/>Ningĩ arutage arĩa mamũkararagia ahooreire, arĩ na mwĩhoko atĩ Ngai no atũme merire, nĩguo mamenye ũhoro wa ma, <verse number="26" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:26 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1TI 3:7">1Tim 3:7</ref></char></note>na atĩ matuĩke a gwĩcookera, na meteithũkie mũtego-inĩ wa mũcukani ũrĩa ũmanyiitĩte mĩgwate nĩguo mekage ũrĩa ekwenda.</para>
  <chapter number="3" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Kwaga Gwĩtigĩra Ngai Matukũ ma Kũrigĩrĩria</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">3:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1TI 4:1">1Tim 4:1</ref>
      </char>
    </note>No rĩrĩ, menya atĩ matukũ ma kũrigĩrĩria nĩgũkagĩa na mahinda ma ũgwati. <verse number="2" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:2 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 1:30">Arom 1:30</ref>; <ref loc="2PE 2:10-12">2Pet 2:10-12</ref></char></note>Andũ magaatuĩka eyendi, na endi mbeeca, na egani, na egaathi, na arumani, na andũ mataiguaga aciari ao, na matarĩ ngaatho, na matarĩ atheru. <verse number="3" style="v"/>Ningĩ makorwo matarĩ na wendani, na matarekanagĩra, na a gũcambania, na matangĩhota kwĩgirĩrĩria merirĩria ma mwĩrĩ, na matarĩ tha, na matendaga maũndũ mega, <verse number="4" style="v"/>na andũ mendaga gũkunyanĩra andũ arĩa angĩ, na arũgĩrĩri, na eĩkĩrĩri, na endi gwĩkenia gũkĩra ũrĩa mendete Ngai. <verse number="5" style="v"/>Andũ acio metuaga ta meyamũrĩire Ngai no nĩmakaanaga hinya wake. Wĩthemage andũ ta acio.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>Acio nĩo arĩa matoonyagĩrĩra nyũmba ciene na makaguucagĩrĩria andũ-a-nja arĩa ahũthũ ngoro, arĩa maiyũrĩtwo nĩ mehia, na arĩa matwaragĩrĩrio nĩ merirĩria mooru ma mĩthemba yothe. <verse number="7" style="v"/>Andũ-a-nja acio nĩmerutaga ũndũ mwerũ hĩndĩ ciothe, no matirĩ hĩndĩ mamenyaga ũhoro ũrĩa wa ma. <verse number="8" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:8 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EXO 7:4">Thaam 7:4</ref>; <ref loc="1TI 6:5">1Tim 6:5</ref></char></note>O ta ũrĩa Janne na Jambare maakararirie Musa-rĩ, no taguo andũ acio mehotoraga makararie ũhoro ũrĩa wa ma. Meciiria mao nĩ mooru, nao ha ũhoro ũkoniĩ wĩtĩkio nĩakũregwo biũ. <verse number="9" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:9 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EXO 7:12">Thaam 7:12</ref></char></note>No rĩrĩ, matingĩthiĩ haraaya, tondũ ũrimũ wao nĩũkamenyeka nĩ andũ othe, o ta ũrĩa ũhoro wa andũ acio wamenyekire.</para>
  <para style="s1">Paũlũ Gũtaara Timotheo</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>No wee-rĩ, nĩũĩ ũhoro wothe wa ũrutani wakwa, na mũtũũrĩre wakwa, na matanya makwa, na wĩtĩkio wakwa, na ũkirĩrĩria wakwa, na wendani wakwa, na kũũmĩrĩria gwakwa, <verse number="11" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:11 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 13:14">Atũm 13:14</ref>; <ref loc="ROM 15:31">Arom 15:31</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 34:19">Thab 34:19</ref></char></note>na kũnyariirwo gwakwa, na mathĩĩna makwa, o na mĩthemba ya maũndũ marĩa maangorire kũu Antiokia, na Ikonia, o na Lusitera, mĩnyamaro ĩrĩa niĩ ndomĩrĩirie. No Mwathani nĩahonokirie kuuma kũrĩ mathĩĩna macio mothe. <verse number="12" style="v"/>Ti-itherũ, mũndũ o wothe ũrĩa ũkwenda gũtũũra mũtũũrĩre wa gũkenia Ngai arĩ thĩinĩ wa Kristũ Jesũ nĩarĩnyariiragwo, <verse number="13" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:13 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2TI 2:16">2Tim 2:16</ref></char></note>No andũ arĩa aaganu na arĩa aheenania nĩmarĩkĩragĩrĩria kwagana, makaheenanagia na makaheenagio. <verse number="14" style="v"/>No wee-rĩ, tũũra wĩkaga maũndũ marĩa wĩrutĩte na ũkametĩkia wega atĩ nĩ ma ma, tondũ nĩũĩ arĩa maakũrutire, <verse number="15" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:15 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 5:39">Joh 5:39</ref>; <ref loc="PSA 119:98-99">Thab 119:98-99</ref></char></note>na ũrĩa wamenyire Maandĩko marĩa matheru kuuma rĩrĩa warĩ kaana,<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">3:15 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">Mwana wa kahĩĩ wa Mũyahudi aambagĩrĩria kwĩruta maandĩko ma Kĩrĩkanĩro kĩrĩa Gĩkũrũ arĩ wa mĩaka ĩtano.</char></note> marĩa mangĩhota gũkũũhĩgia nĩguo ũkaahonokio nĩ ũndũ wa gwĩtĩkia thĩinĩ wa Kristũ Jesũ. <verse number="16" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:16 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2PE 1:20">2Pet 1:20</ref>, <ref loc="2PE 1:21">21</ref>; <ref loc="DEU 29:29">Gũcook 29:29</ref></char></note>Ũhoro wothe ũrĩa wandĩkĩtwo Maandĩko-inĩ wekĩrirwo thĩinĩ wa mũwandĩki nĩ Ngai, na nĩwagĩrĩire harĩ ũhoro wa kũrutana, na wa gũkaanania, na wa kũrũnga mahĩtia, o na wa kũrutana mĩikarĩre ya ũthingu, <verse number="17" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:17 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1TI 6:11">1Tim 6:11</ref>; <ref loc="2TI 2:21">2Tim 2:21</ref></char></note>nĩgeetha mũndũ wa Ngai akoragwo arĩ mũkinyanĩru, na athagathagĩtwo biũ kũruta wĩra o wothe mwega.</para>
  <chapter number="4" style="c"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ACT 10:42">Atũm 10:42</ref>; <ref loc="1TI 5:21">1Tim 5:21</ref></char>
    </note>Atĩrĩrĩ, niĩ ndĩ mbere ya Ngai na ya Kristũ Jesũ, ũrĩa ũgaatuĩra ciira andũ arĩa marĩ muoyo na arĩa makuĩte, na nĩ ũndũ wa gũũka gwake na ũthamaki wake-rĩ, ngũgũtaara atĩrĩ: <verse number="2" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:2 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1TI 4:13">1Tim 4:13</ref>; <ref loc="1TI 5:20">1Tim 5:20</ref></char></note>Hunjagia Ũhoro wa Ngai; ikaraga wĩhaarĩirie hĩndĩ ĩrĩa yagĩrĩire na ĩrĩa ĩtagĩrĩire; ningĩ rũithagĩria andũ mahĩtia mao, na ũmakaanagie, na ũmomagĩrĩrie, wĩ na ũkirĩrĩria mũnene na ũrutani mũbarĩrĩre. <verse number="3" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:3 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1TI 1:10">1Tim 1:10</ref></char></note>Nĩgũkorwo ihinda nĩrĩgooka rĩrĩa andũ makaaregana na ũrutani ũrĩa wagĩrĩire. No nĩguo mahingie merirĩria mao-rĩ, nĩmakeyũnganĩria arutani aingĩ nĩguo mameerage maũndũ marĩa matũ mao mekwenda kũigua. <verse number="4" style="v"/>Nĩmakahũgũra matũ mao matige kũigua ũhoro wa ma, na magarũrũkĩre ngʼano cia tũhũ. <verse number="5" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:5 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 21:8">Atũm 21:8</ref></char></note>No wee-rĩ, ikaraga wĩiguĩte maũndũ-inĩ mothe, na ũmĩrĩrie kũnyariirwo, ningĩ rutaga wĩra wa kũhunjia ũhoro wa Ngai, na ũhingagie mawĩra mothe ma ũtungata waku.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:6 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PHP 1:23">Afil 1:23</ref>; <ref loc="PHP 2:17">Afil 2:17</ref></char>
    </note>Nĩgũkorwo nĩnyambĩrĩirie gũitwo thĩ ta iruta rĩa kũnyuuo, narĩo ihinda rĩakwa rĩa kuuma gũkũ nĩrĩkinyu. <verse number="7" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:7 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1TI 1:18">1Tim 1:18</ref>; <ref loc="1CO 9:24">1Akor 9:24</ref></char></note>Nĩndũĩte mbaara ĩrĩa njega, narĩo ihenya rĩakwa rĩgakinya mũthia, o na nĩndũũrĩte menyereire wĩtĩkio wakwa. <verse number="8" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:8 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2TI 1:12">2Tim 1:12</ref>; <ref loc="1TI 6:14">1Tim 6:14</ref></char></note>Rĩu nĩnjigĩirwo thũmbĩ ĩrĩa ya ũthingu, ĩrĩa Mwathani, ũrĩa ũtuaga ciira na kĩhooto, akaahe mũthenya ũcio, na to niĩ nyiki akaahe, no ningĩ nĩ andũ othe arĩa makoretwo merirĩirie kũguũranĩrio gwake.</para>
  <para style="s1">Maũndũ ma Paũlũ Mwene</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>Geria mũno o ũrĩa wahota ũũke kũrĩ niĩ na ihenya, <verse number="10" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:10 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="COL 4:14">Akol 4:14</ref></char></note>nĩgũkorwo Dema, tondũ wa kwenda maũndũ ma thĩ ĩno, nĩandiganĩirie na agathiĩ Thesalonike. Nake Keresike nĩathiĩte Galatia, na Tito agathiĩ Dalamatia. <verse number="11" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:11 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="COL 4:14">Akol 4:14</ref></char></note>Luka nowe tũrĩ nake gũkũ. Oya Mariko mũũke nake, tondũ nĩ ũteithio harĩ niĩ ũtungata-inĩ wakwa. <verse number="12" style="v"/>Nĩndatũmire Tukiko kũu Efeso. <verse number="13" style="v"/>Ũgĩũka-rĩ, ndehera kabuti karĩa ndatigire gwa Karipo kũrĩa Teroa, na ũndehere mabuku makwa ma gĩkũnjo, na makĩria njũa iria cia kwandĩkwo.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:14 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ACT 19:33">Atũm 19:33</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Alekisandero ũrĩa mũturi wa indo cia rũthuku nĩanjĩkire ũũru mũno. Mwathani nĩwe ũkaamũrĩha kũringana na ciĩko ciake. <verse number="15" style="v"/>O nawe mwĩmenyerere, tondũ nĩakararirie ndũmĩrĩri iitũ na hinya.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:16 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ACT 7:60">Atũm 7:60</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Hĩndĩ ĩrĩa ndaciirithirio rĩa mbere-rĩ, gũtirĩ mũndũ wokire kũndeithia, andũ othe nĩmandiganĩirie. Maroaga gũtuĩrwo ũũru. <verse number="17" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:17 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PHP 4:13">Afil 4:13</ref>; <ref loc="1SA 17:37">1Sam 17:37</ref></char></note>No Mwathani nĩarũgamire na niĩ na akĩnjĩkĩra hinya, nĩgeetha ndũmĩrĩri ĩhunjio biũ nĩ ũndũ wakwa na andũ-a-Ndũrĩrĩ othe mamĩigue. Na niĩ ngĩhonokio kuuma kanua ka mũrũũthi. <verse number="18" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:18 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PSA 121:7">Thab 121:7</ref></char></note>Mwathani nĩakahonokia ũũru-inĩ o wothe, na andware ũthamaki-inĩ wake wa igũrũ, nake arogoocagwo tene na tene. Ameni.</para>
  <para style="s1">Ngeithi cia Mũthia</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v"/>Geithia Pirisila na Akula, na andũ a nyũmba ya Onesiforo. <verse number="20" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:20 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 19:22">Atũm 19:22</ref></char></note>Erasito aatigirwo Korinitho, na niĩ ngĩtiga Terefimo kũu Mileto arĩ mũrũaru. <verse number="21" style="v"/>Geria ũkinye gũkũ mbere ya ihinda rĩa heho. Nĩwageithio nĩ Eubulu, o na Pudene, na Lino, na Kilaudia, na ariũ na aarĩ a Ithe witũ othe.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:22 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GAL 6:18">Agal 6:18</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Mwathani aroikaria roho waku. Wega wa Ngai ũroikara hamwe nawe.</para>
</usx>
